<Group labelreference="L195" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle17" layout="_pstyle179">Non-linear differential equations with three dimensions: chaos</Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L1478" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">We will use the Lorenz equations as an example</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L2272" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">restart; with(plots): with(DEtools):</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L2273" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"> define functions</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L2269" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">f1 := (x,y,z) -&gt; sigma * (y - x);</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">f2 := (x,y,z) -&gt; -x * z + r * x - y;</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">f3 := (x,y,z) -&gt;  x * y - b * z;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L2270" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">define differential equations</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L198" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">DE1 := diff(x(t),t) = f1(x(t),y(t),z(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">DE2 := diff(y(t),t) = f2(x(t),y(t),z(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">DE3 := diff(z(t),t) = f3(x(t),y(t),z(t));</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">DE := DE1, DE2, DE3;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L1479" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">define parameters</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L1481" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">r:=28; b:=8/3; sigma:=10;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L1483" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">define two initial conditions close to each other</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L200" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">ic1 := x(0)=2,     y(0)=5,z(0)=5;</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">ic2 := x(0)=2.0001,y(0)=5,z(0)=5;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L201" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150">Solve system with dsolve. The option maxfun=-1 allows maple to go beyond the default 30,000 function evaluations.</Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150">To see more options we refer to the help.</Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle150"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L202" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">sol1 := dsolve({DE,ic1},[x(t),y(t),z(t)],type=numeric,maxfun=-1);</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle154">sol2 := dsolve({DE,ic2},[x(t),y(t),z(t)],type=numeric,maxfun=-1);</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
